3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes algorithms for finding the optimal solution in a distributed and low-complexity manner, which involves system design and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper mentions simulation results, which may involve multimedia applications. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of cognitive systems, which may involve artificial intelligence techniques.
